1942;;Sex Hygiene;;American;;Otto Brower, John Ford;;George Reeves, Richard Derr;;docudrama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sex_Hygiene;;Several servicemen relax by playing pool at their base. One later visits a prostitute and contracts syphilis. As a result of his unfortunate experience, there is an opportunity for sexual health information about syphilis, how it is spread and how its spread can be prevented.